Comment: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:38.10,Alternative,Girl,0,0,0,,Tsurugi likes you, Ohana.
Comment: 1,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}OP FRAME 1 — TL
Comment: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}OP FRAME 1 — TL II
Comment: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:41.87,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Ko!
Comment: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:42.87,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Ohana...
Comment: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:46.41,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Ohana!
Comment: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:47.62,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Ko!
Comment: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:50.79,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing here?!
Comment: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:54.42,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I... Well...
Comment: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:56.72,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,The Kissui Inn is...
Comment: 0,0:01:57.51,0:01:58.51,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,What about it?
Comment: 0,0:01:58.51,0:01:59.89,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why...
Comment: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:01.80,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do you...
Comment: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:05.56,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,It seems like the Kissui Inn is going to be closing soon...
Comment: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:07.64,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}...have such kind eyes?
Comment: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:14.61,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Ohana?!
Comment: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:23.16,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Have you calmed down a bit?
Comment: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.12,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:30.79,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Ko, you get the corn kernels out\N of these soups in a weird way, right?
Comment: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:33.00,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Don't you pour water in it,
Comment: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,pour the entire thing into a cup, then pick it out with chopsticks?
Comment: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:40.05,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,I... stopped doing that.
Comment: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:40.80,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:44.93,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,I just leave the corn I can't get in there.
Comment: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:47.89,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Huh? But it'll rot.
Comment: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:50.60,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,No it won't. It won't ever change.
Comment: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:56.86,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Remember when you said that\N the scenery in Tokyo was boring?
Comment: 0,0:02:56.86,0:03:00.32,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,I'd never even thought that in my life.
Comment: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:04.99,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,But after you left...
Comment: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the scenery's been nothing but boring for me.
Comment: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:10.00,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Ko...
Comment: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:15.46,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Your mom showed me the video of you working at the Kissui Inn.
Comment: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:16.75,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,My mom?!
Comment: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:18.80,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,I was really surprised.
Comment: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:23.97,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,I've never been there, so I didn't know anything about it.
Comment: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:27.43,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,But you were there, and just because of that,
Comment: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt as though I'd seen it before.
Comment: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:36.65,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,I think that I enjoyed the scenery here because you were here, too.
Comment: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.69,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not too swift on the uptake.
Comment: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:42.49,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Listen, I've been really frustrated.
Comment: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:44.24,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,I felt like you left me behind.
Comment: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.41,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's obvious enough...
Comment: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:48.83,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,I felt as though you picked the Kissui Inn over me.
Comment: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:50.83,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}...for even me to understand...
Comment: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:55.46,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,But after seeing it, I kind of started liking the Kissui Inn.
Comment: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:56.59,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,So...
Comment: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:58.00,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}...Ko's feelings...
Comment: 0,0:03:58.00,0:03:59.80,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,So...
Comment: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:02.26,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and what he's about to say.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:05.59,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,I don't know what kind of\N misunderstandings you have in your head,
Comment: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:06.89,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,but I...
Comment: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:17.11,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Ohana?
Comment: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:20.40,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you—
Comment: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:24.07,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Don't say all these things!
Comment: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:25.45,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I want to say them!
Comment: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:29.49,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'm the one who wants to say things to you!
Comment: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:32.41,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Listen, I...
Comment: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.50,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I...
Comment: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:36.75,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I...
Comment: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:39.25,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I want...
Comment: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:40.67,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Want...
Comment: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:43.67,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I want you to come to the Bonbori Festival!
Comment: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.68,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Sure.
Comment: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:51.68,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Comment: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:54.94,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,I will.
Comment: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.15,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Hey, Ohana!
Comment: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:04.20,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Don't cry.
Comment: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:07.32,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Ohana!
Comment: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:09.78,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}I realized that the scenery I'd always found to be boring...
Comment: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:12.79,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}The scenery that has Ko in it,
Comment: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:14.83,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}was so beautiful.
Comment: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:19.54,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yes, okay.
Comment: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.80,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'll be going on ahead, Aun—
Comment: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.47,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I mean, Sis.
Comment: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.76,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Don't you want to see your mom?
Comment: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:31.76,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Nah, not yet.
Comment: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:38.15,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Not until I decide what I want to do.
Comment: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:01.46,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,All right!
Comment: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.40,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Hey.
Comment: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:27.36,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I figured I should learn lots of\N stuff from you before you quit.
Comment: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:30.36,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,If only I'd been more competent,
Comment: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,things wouldn't have turned out this way.
Comment: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:43.29,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Ohana and Takako still aren't back...
Comment: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:44.30,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Comment: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:50.51,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,It's the tourist season, but we only have\N reservations during the Bonbori Festival...
Comment: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:53.55,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Maybe we really are done.
Comment: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:56.89,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,You can leave for school now.
Comment: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.18,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Oh, but...
Comment: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:03.73,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Hello, you've reached the Kissui Inn.
Comment: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:05.36,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.24,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,What are you dozing off for?
Comment: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:12.45,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Comment: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:17.91,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Mr. Ren's shift is over early tonight, right?
Comment: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.41,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:22.96,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,He says he's going out drinking with the\N owner of the next inn he'll be working at.
Comment: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:25.50,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,When you're as good as\N Mr. Ren, every inn wants to have you.
Comment: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:27.92,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,W-What about you?
Comment: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:33.68,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,To be honest, I've been invited along with him.
Comment: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:36.47,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Minko?
Comment: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:38.85,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Hey!
Comment: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:40.60,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Did you cut your hand? Let me see.
Comment: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:45.06,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,You're fine. Don't scare me—
Comment: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:47.27,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Are you guys going to leave me behind?
Comment: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:50.65,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Well, they're not going to hire someone who's underage...
Comment: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:52.36,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Comment: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:54.32,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,What indeed...
Comment: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:55.32,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,What should...
Comment: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:04.00,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,One man, and one knife!
Comment: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:06.34,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,I'll train my cooking skills no matter where I am!
Comment: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:10.59,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:12.97,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,It's a line from a comic I used to—
Comment: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:14.34,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,"Teppei, the Wandering Chef"!
Comment: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:16.22,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Y-You know it?
Comment: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:20.39,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Yes! Teppei was the one who\N inspired me to become a chef!
Comment: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:21.23,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Comment: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:25.06,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Wow! These bring back so many memories!
Comment: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:26.77,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Dude, the Tuna Bowl!
Comment: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:31.32,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Yeah! He leaps into the ocean\N because he says it tastes best when it's alive!
Comment: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:34.15,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,He duels with a swimming tuna in the sea!
Comment: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:35.53,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,And then he makes a meal out of it!
Comment: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:39.03,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, it's pretty gruesome.
Comment: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:43.12,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Yeah? I thought it was a pretty good idea...
Comment: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:49.34,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Huh? You were also a fan of this?
Comment: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:51.55,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Actually, the person who wrote this...
Comment: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:52.88,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,was me.
Comment: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.51,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,What?!
Comment: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:01.39,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,What?!
Comment: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:05.39,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,When I was starving, an editor friend of mine encouraged me.
Comment: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:06.98,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,I wrote a draft.
Comment: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:09.94,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Well, even though this comic didn't really sell...
Comment: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:12.74,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,I still kind of like it.
Comment: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.99,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,I've always been inspired by Teppei...
Comment: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:18.78,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,So the one who determined my future was...
Comment: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:20.28,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,this perverted freak?!
Comment: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:22.04,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Comment: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:24.04,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,You want an autograph? Do you—
Comment: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:26.42,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,There you are!
Comment: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:27.92,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,It's a crisis, guys!
Comment: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:32.92,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:48.77,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yo!
Comment: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:56.65,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know what's going to happen to the Kissui Inn,{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:58.86,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I'm going to stay until the very end,{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}even if there aren't any customers.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:03.99,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Comment: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:06.21,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm... home?
Comment: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:05.33,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,We appear to be fully booked on the 8th...
Comment: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:07.08,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Yes, please give me a second.
Comment: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:08.12,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Nako?
Comment: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:10.63,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, only the Wave Room is open on the 8th...
Comment: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:12.09,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Hello, you've reached the Kissui Inn!
Comment: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:14.67,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Mr. Ren, ten customers are booked for the 7th!
Comment: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:17.38,Default,Renji,0,0,0,,Which means the meals will be...
Comment: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:20.34,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,That customer can't eat abalone or tuna!
Comment: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:19.93,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes, you've reached the Kissui Inn.
Comment: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:21.47,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's a fax.
Comment: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:21.93,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,No tuna?!
Comment: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.35,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Uh...
Comment: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:24.89,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Oh, Ohana!
Comment: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:25.93,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Quick, help us!
Comment: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Reservations just started popping up out of nowhere...
Comment: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:29.44,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Comment: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:31.06,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,What's this ruckus?
Comment: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:32.36,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Madam Manager!
Comment: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.03,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Check this out!
Comment: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.28,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome back!
Comment: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:38.28,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,This is a magazine I bought at the airport.
Comment: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:42.16,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,The Kissui Inn is on the opening\N page and we got an amazing review!
Comment: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:43.37,Default,All,0,0,0,,What?!
Comment: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:44.83,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Comment: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:46.83,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Hey, let me see!
Comment: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:53.34,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Did you have breakfast, Miss Satsuki?
Comment: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.75,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Comment: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:55.92,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Comment: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:57.42,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Where would you like to eat?
Comment: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:58.55,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,I'd like some wine.
Comment: 0,0:10:58.55,0:10:59.59,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:01.22,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that?
Comment: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:04.64,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Comment: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:07.68,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,"They put so much effort into every detail of comfort,
Comment: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:10.73,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,and their meals are comparable to those of famous restaurants"!
Comment: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:11.90,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Comment: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:14.27,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,But when did they visit us?
Comment: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:16.48,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Another undercover person?
Comment: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:18.53,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Who cares about that?!
Comment: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:20.15,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,We can do it.
Comment: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.95,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Now we can do this.
Comment: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:23.16,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Young master...
Comment: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:24.87,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,The Kissui Inn!
Comment: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:26.66,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,If we start grabbing customers with this,
Comment: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.50,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,we might even be able to rebuild this place!
Comment: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:30.83,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Comment: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:33.88,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Let's use this as the start to—
Comment: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:35.09,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,No.
Comment: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:38.09,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,The Kissui Inn will close after the Bonbori Festival.
Comment: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:40.59,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,It's already been decided. That's that.
Comment: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:41.93,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Madam Manager...
Comment: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.01,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,But why?!
Comment: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:44.85,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,The calls for reservations are coming nonstop!
Comment: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:48.81,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Why should we quit when we have the wind at our back?!
Comment: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:50.31,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Mr. Ren,
Comment: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:56.15,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I heard that you've already secured a\N spot at the Hatago Inn, along with Tohru.
Comment: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:57.32,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Um, I'm free...
Comment: 0,0:11:57.32,0:12:01.65,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,And I hear a small restaurant in\N town is trying to scout you, Tomoe.
Comment: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:03.32,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I-Is that true?
Comment: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:06.91,Default,Renji,0,0,0,,I'll call them and cancel our offer.
Comment: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:05.28,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, I'm...
Comment: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:09.58,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,We want to work here!
Comment: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:12.04,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Yeah! As long as this place can continue running—
Comment: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:16.25,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Don't trouble your next workplace for selfish reasons.
Comment: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:17.96,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,You're the one being selfish!
Comment: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:20.38,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,We...
Comment: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:23.01,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,We don't want to leave the Kissui Inn!
Comment: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:25.51,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Why are you being so stubborn?
Comment: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:29.06,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,"It's already been decided"? What—
Comment: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:31.35,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Get back to work.
Comment: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:32.18,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Madam Manager!
Comment: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:38.44,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Don't accept any more reservations. Do you hear me?
Comment: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:42.07,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Madam Manager...
Comment: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:52.16,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I wonder if the young master\N and the others are still discussing...
Comment: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.62,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:57.33,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,They said they're thinking of a way to convince the Madam Manager.
Comment: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:00.46,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,I wonder what she's thinking.
Comment: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone says they want to stay here.
Comment: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:04.63,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:06.93,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,She's so mean...
Comment: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:07.89,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Nakochi?
Comment: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.31,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Everyone loves the Kissui Inn!
Comment: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:14.35,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Things are finally looking up, and she's...
Comment: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She's being so mean!
Comment: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:17.27,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Nakochi's angry?!
Comment: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:19.73,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I'm going to talk to her—
Comment: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:24.70,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,M-Madam Manager?!
Comment: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:42.21,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,That was fast!
Comment: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:56.35,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,N-Nakochi!
Comment: 0,0:13:57.60,0:14:00.44,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,U-Um, about this morning...
Comment: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:01.69,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I...
Comment: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:09.66,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Um, there's something I want to...
Comment: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:22.67,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,The Madam Manager...
Comment: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:24.00,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,She bathes really fast,
Comment: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:28.01,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,and this place is cleaner than it was before she came in...
Comment: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:31.05,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'll talk to her!
Comment: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:32.05,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Ohana...
Comment: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:41.10,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Madam Manager!
Comment: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:42.27,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Why are you so fast?!
Comment: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:43.15,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Ohana.
Comment: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:44.15,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yes?!
Comment: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:45.73,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Don't be busy tomorrow.
Comment: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:46.78,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:53.58,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Ohana and the Madam Manager?
Comment: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:55.16,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:56.70,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,They left early this morning.
Comment: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:58.37,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,To where?!
Comment: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:00.92,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,It's going to be busy this weekend.
Comment: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:04.67,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Oh, and she said to send someone to the Bonbori Festival
Comment: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,in the late afternoon to help with preparations.
Comment: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:08.51,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,The Bonbori Festival?!
Comment: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:09.80,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,That's low on the priority list!
Comment: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:14.10,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,As I thought, the Madam Manager won't budge.
Comment: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:20.64,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Hello, you've reached the Kissui Inn.
Comment: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:25.65,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry, reservations for next week are...
Comment: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:29.90,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sorry about that.
Comment: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:30.78,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Reservation for the 9th?
Comment: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:32.20,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Of course we're open.
Comment: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.66,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Yes, a room for three?
Comment: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.12,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you very much!
Comment: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:36.66,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Young master...
Comment: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:40.33,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I don't know what she's being so stubborn about,
Comment: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:41.75,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,but we have to convince her!
Comment: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:43.13,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:46.13,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,The Kissui Inn can operate without her orders.
Comment: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:47.55,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Enishing...
Comment: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:09.15,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Grab a wet cloth.
Comment: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:10.53,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:21.62,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,He'd be so disappointed if he were alive.
Comment: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:22.21,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:25.50,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,It wasn't possible to get them back,
Comment: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:29.46,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,the days we were full of dreams...
Comment: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:32.59,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,The busy days where everyone was so focused on work...
Comment: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:34.68,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,"It wasn't possible"?
Comment: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:36.05,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,We still don't know that—
Comment: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:37.93,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,You don't need to pay the burden.
Comment: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:45.15,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,He and I started the Kissui Inn out of nothing.
Comment: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:48.15,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,We didn't know anything about running an inn.
Comment: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.36,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,But the Kissui Inn is different now.
Comment: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:54.07,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,It's full of the traverses we've made.
Comment: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:55.82,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,It's not nothing anymore.
Comment: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll take a while to even get to nothing.
Comment: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:01.37,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Are you talking about money?
Comment: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:04.71,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Everyone's already begun walking their own paths.
Comment: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:08.21,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,There's no need for you all to be stuck with our dreams.
Comment: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:10.55,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,You can start from nothing—
Comment: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:11.51,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,No.
Comment: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:14.97,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,We all love the Kissui Inn!
Comment: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:17.64,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,We can't turn that feeling into nothing!
Comment: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:21.18,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,The inn doesn't just belong to the two of you anymore!
Comment: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:23.85,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,We all want to work here.
Comment: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It might even become our dreams, too!
Comment: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:38.28,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Madam Manager?!
Comment: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:42.58,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,Hello?
Comment: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:43.20,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,It's me.
Comment: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:44.66,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,Oh, Enishi.
Comment: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:48.58,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Thank you oh so very much\N for having pity on the Kissui Inn.
Comment: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:50.34,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,I didn't.
Comment: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:53.09,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,I just did my job and wrote everything I actually felt.
Comment: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:56.05,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,And besides, all it created was an opportunity.
Comment: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:58.01,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,Just a small oppo—
Comment: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:00.93,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I'll use this as an opportunity to\N have customers return more often.
Comment: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:05.81,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I won't be in your shadow forever.
Comment: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:06.98,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Comment: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:10.40,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I'll make the Kissui Inn popular.
Comment: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:11.73,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Bye.
Comment: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.45,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Comment: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:24.37,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,It's fine. Please rest for a while.
Comment: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:26.29,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,I'll leave some tea here.
Comment: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:27.71,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Comment: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:30.33,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I was so worried.
Comment: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd have to be hospitalized again.
Comment: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:35.46,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I'm just a little tired.
Comment: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:43.97,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,This isn't the first time I\N thought about shutting down the inn.
Comment: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:44.93,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:50.35,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I realized it when Satsuki ran\N away, saying she wouldn't succeed me.
Comment: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:53.94,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,"An inn to make Sui happy."
Comment: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:55.65,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,That's what it was.
Comment: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:59.03,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I wanted to realize my dream with him.
Comment: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:05.87,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I made Satsuki and Enishi endure so much just for my selfishness.
Comment: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:10.50,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I sacrificed them for my own happiness.
Comment: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:12.04,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Madam Manager...
Comment: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:15.71,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Enishi decided to be the successor,
Comment: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,even though there were other things he wanted to do.
Comment: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:24.64,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,He, Satsuki, and I have all been stubborn since Satsuki had left.
Comment: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:30.77,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,We were all focused on the Kissui Inn.
Comment: 0,0:19:31.39,0:19:33.19,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,But that isn't right.
Comment: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:36.98,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Enishi isn't fit for this kind of work.
Comment: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:43.11,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,And so, all of the workers will suffer because of it.
Comment: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:47.54,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,If Enishi and the workers are going to be unhappy,
Comment: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:50.83,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I just want to free them.
Comment: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:55.21,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I want to free them of his and my dream.
Comment: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:59.84,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,You're old, aren't you?
Comment: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:04.47,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,You shouldn't get up!
Comment: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:06.30,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Ohana, you...
Comment: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:11.23,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I said that because I don't really get what you're saying.
Comment: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:16.02,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I thought perhaps it's really hard to\N understand what old people are saying.
Comment: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:22.78,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Madam Manager?
Comment: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:24.74,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Sheesh, you're so...
Comment: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:32.21,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Though I don't understand you, my anger towards you is gone.
Comment: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:37.75,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I can't agree to it, but I'll fest it up anyway!
Comment: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:39.34,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Until the Bonbori Festival!
Comment: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:45.80,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm counting on you.
Comment: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.35,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Comment: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:52.98,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:55.98,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,What is this about?
Comment: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:59.86,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,Everyone in the union is supposed\N to help out with the Bonbori Festival.
Comment: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:04.32,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,It's unforgivable for only the Kissui Inn to not participate.
Comment: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:05.61,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,We're sorry.
Comment: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:09.49,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,We have so many reservations, so we're still preparing...
Comment: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:12.25,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,This is what happens when a magazine features you.
Comment: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:13.79,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Hey—
Comment: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:15.21,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry.
Comment: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:16.50,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Madam Manager!
Comment: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:18.46,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,We'll send someone to help, too.
Comment: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:21.50,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I don't care who, stop what you're doing and go help.
Comment: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:28.34,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,You guys...
Comment: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:33.35,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I-I'll go.
Comment: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:34.77,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Ohana!
Comment: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:35.64,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,No.
Comment: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:38.31,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Go.
Comment: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:39.69,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:45.03,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Ohana...
Comment: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:46.57,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,Well, then.
Comment: 0,0:23:31.72,0:23:33.51,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,The Kissui Inn will change.
Comment: 0,0:23:33.51,0:23:36.89,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Give back the Kissui Inn I love!
Comment: 1,0:23:38.89,0:23:41.39,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Is work really about winning or losing?
